# Docket project

Personal job application tracker for Baseer. Standalone: own DB, no login (fixed OWNER_ID), own deployment.

- Domains: `docket.baseer.co.uk` / `docket-staging.baseer.co.uk`
- API: `docket-api.humzab1711.workers.dev` (custom `docket-api.baseer.co.uk` when attached)
- Zone: `baseer.co.uk` Cloudflare account (single-level subdomains, Universal SSL)
- npm workspaces + Turborepo only — never pnpm/yarn
- Free Cloudflare tier: no Containers, Queues, or Advanced Certificate Manager
- Canonical agent docs: `AGENTS.md`. Sync rules with `npm run rules:sync`.
